ZH: 我喜歡在菜裡加一點辣椒。
EN: I like to add a bit of chili pepper to my dishes.

ZH: 辣椒可以讓食物更加美味。
EN: Chili pepper can make the food more delicious.

ZH: 這道菜裡有很多辣椒，可能會很辣。
EN: There are a lot of chili peppers in this dish, it might be very spicy.

ZH: 辣椒有很多種不同的品種。
EN: There are many different varieties of chili peppers.

ZH: 我的媽媽做的麻婆豆腐很辣，放了很多辣椒。
EN: The Mapo tofu my mom makes is very spicy, she puts a lot of chili peppers in it.

ZH: 我不太能吃辣椒，因為我胃不太好。
EN: I can't eat chili peppers too much because my stomach is not good.

ZH: 吃辣椒可以讓人感覺很暖和。
EN: Eating chili peppers can make people feel warm.

ZH: 辣椒是一種很健康的調味料。
EN: Chili pepper is a very healthy seasoning.

ZH: 看起來像辣椒，但其實是甜椒。
EN: It looks like a chili pepper, but it's actually a bell pepper.

